{"tid":1404921,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"八五會去荃灣嘅同我入來！！","createTime":"2019-08-04T06:43:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T16:32:33.000Z","uid":212944,"like":35,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"cbab2979d5354f4bc23188d32028306b3807bf13","tid":1404921,"uid":212944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T06:43:32.000Z","msg":"利申，住咗荃灣廿鳩幾年。細個係荃灣仲有家樂福，荃灣廣場仲有噴水池個陣。街坊先知我講咩～ <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有幾樣野要留意返：<br />\n1. 荃灣市中心兩邊有兩間狗屋，一間近大窩口，係新界南總部，一間近荃景圍<br />\n2. 綠楊新邨有兩座紀律部隊宿舍，成條邨多藍絲，上屆區議會係新民主同盟唯一輸咗嘅選區<br />\n3. 好多廢老大媽，之前有好撚多個撐警街站<br />\n4. 好撚多天橋，好易畀班狗做制高點<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n雖然係咁，我認為荃灣係玩得過，而且識玩可以好好玩。<br />\n<br />\n- 打遊擊，不停set路障佔路，唔使死守，班狗要通路都有排通。沙咀道大河道眾安街楊屋道，慢慢玩。就算唔set路障，只要有油喺路面，都無得通車，千祈唔好咁做。我地良好市民唔犯法嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n- 萬一狗真係來到，大家除咗可以經大窩口散去葵芳，仲可以極速散入各大商場，荃新天地荃灣廣場城市中心，即管睇佢就唔就膽重演新城市廣場困獸鬥<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n暫時諗到咁多，大家點睇？"},{"pid":"b45f692e7a15fce1297f7a357a9ddbadda650fc2","tid":1404921,"uid":212944,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T06:43:50.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n我會罷工"},{"pid":"96f5b7f31da50a0768ed3027b0f22ec9f5213993","tid":1404921,"uid":212944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T06:44:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e1584060f7e31386829e6da180ef59564e016824","tid":1404921,"uid":212944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T06:46:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c85902103f3dfca06da0d9f24b3eb3ccf2405bb3","tid":1404921,"uid":212944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T06:46:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f9f83529daa31ffb934675d2431a1ae5be1ee491","tid":1404921,"uid":34383,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T06:50:02.000Z","msg":"希望聽日葵青ching 都黎守護荃灣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"289a73e473eaf85d5aefbeadcbb1c8c88dd8abd0","tid":1404921,"uid":212944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T06:50:42.000Z","msg":"大家一齊討論下<br />\n認同請推"},{"pid":"2ba7bc7e1d79b61c47106dfa546e1e0b6461de57","tid":1404921,"uid":4855,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T06:53:46.000Z","msg":"近年新起條天橋 一直都傳施工不良<br />\n今鋪應該引曬d狗上去試一試磅"},{"pid":"6e6afbe489643db0677ef4e30560a239f2e93f2f","tid":1404921,"uid":253174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T06:55:37.000Z","msg":"大把商場你玩"},{"pid":"79d3b329865989375a4c627396eba89da0649bce","tid":1404921,"uid":68896,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2ba7bc7e1d79b61c47106dfa546e1e0b6461de57","tid":1404921,"uid":4855,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T06:53:46.000Z","msg":"近年新起條天橋 一直都傳施工不良<br />\n今鋪應該引曬d狗上去試一試磅"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T06:57:59.000Z","msg":"行襯都feel到佢震緊<br />\n<br />\n第一次行過仲以為自己頭暈腳浮浮"},{"pid":"8ae87eb39f67a9d9782f3496c877d883d7abeb4a","tid":1404921,"uid":269681,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T07:04:01.000Z","msg":"荃灣識玩真係好玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但可唔可在避開下沙咀道大會堂個頭 好多獸醫診所<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />人都怕既催淚煙 我怕貓貓狗狗都頂唔住"},{"pid":"88ede6ab6c6775c556e100d264d7cf09969c140f","tid":1404921,"uid":185449,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f9f83529daa31ffb934675d2431a1ae5be1ee491","tid":1404921,"uid":34383,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T06:50:02.000Z","msg":"希望聽日葵青ching 都黎守護荃灣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T07:09:41.000Z","msg":"當然<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1586fa4fb7c491258d649ecca4ddee0275397b9","tid":1404921,"uid":64003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T07:10:38.000Z","msg":"一時又話唔比影相 一時又上嚟求相 你玩曬啦<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1404604\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1404604</a><br />\n